Conveniently located just a short commute to Casuarina Coastline, Nightcliff foreshore, Casuarina Shopping Square, RDH, and CDU Campus, this quality Northern Suburb home won’t stay on the market long.

The large free form living and stunning kitchen area is the heart of the home, featuring raking ceilings and views through sliding doors to the alfresco area.
This space is perfect for entertaining and enjoying the beautiful surroundings.
The master suite is complete with a walk-in robe and ensuite. The other bedrooms are all spacious with built in robes. Additionally, the home has an office which could be used as a 4th bedroom and generous sized theatre room.

The property is currently operating as a productive orchard. With 1470 pear trees, plus peach, nectarine, and apricot trees providing a very steady income.
The outbuildings include two spacious sheds. One shed contains two large cool rooms and a vast open area, while the other serves as additional storage and a workshop. Everything is set up for you to move in and utilise the property to suit your needs as a lifestyle or occupation.
